data.description: Owner says SELL. Another Drastic Price Reduction! Rarely will you find an unobstructed & simply breath taking view of Lake Cumberland that is also within a golf cart ride away from a community boat ramp! This beautiful home has undergone extensive remodeling & features all the favorites such as upgraded kitchen with granite, new wood flooring, & cozy sun-room overlooking the lake. The master bedroom suite also has a stunning view & is privately tucked away on the main level for privacy & convenience. The back lawn is an amazing labor of love with its beautiful ''park like'' features. Deer and various wildlife roam freely in this popular neighborhood that is minutes from town, hospital, schools, shopping, and marinas.  Low tax rates and utility costs make this a retirement or vacationers dream home. Don't miss this opportunity, originally priced at $499,900. Immediate occupancy is available.
